00:14:08,499 --> 00:14:11,299
<font color="#00ff00">There's a framed platinum disc</font>
<font color="#00ff00">on the wall.</font>

234
00:14:18,379 --> 00:14:22,779
<font color="#00ffff">So, what do you</font>
<font color="#00ffff">make of it, Inspector?</font>

235
00:14:22,819 --> 00:14:24,299
<font color="#00ffff">Inspector?</font>

236
00:14:24,339 --> 00:14:26,099
<font color="#00ffff">In... Inspec...?</font>

237
00:14:26,139 --> 00:14:27,339
<font color="#00ffff">Where's he gone?</font>

238
00:14:28,899 --> 00:14:30,179
<font color="#00ffff">Inspector!</font>

239
00:14:31,859 --> 00:14:33,179
Gloves.

240
00:14:35,259 --> 00:14:40,419
I want to see what gift our Santa
