<font color="#ffff00">Sir, look.</font>

255
00:15:31,699 --> 00:15:35,459
<font color="#ffff00">10:15 - the same time our first</font>
<font color="#ffff00">victim was shot.</font>

256
00:15:35,499 --> 00:15:36,579
For real?

257
00:15:36,619 --> 00:15:39,659
<font color="#00ffff">If both murders</font>
<font color="#00ffff">happened at the same time,</font>

258
00:15:39,699 --> 00:15:43,219
<font color="#00ffff">then we're dealing</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with two separate killers.</font>

