00:15:43,259 --> 00:15:46,859
Who seemingly agreed to kill their
victims at the exact same time,

260
00:15:46,899 --> 00:15:50,659
in the exact same manner,
wearing the exact same costumes.

261
00:15:53,779 --> 00:15:54,899
Interesting.

262
00:16:00,659 --> 00:16:03,819
<font color="#00ffff">I just wanted to say that we</font>
<font color="#00ffff">appreciate you agreeing</font>

263
00:16:03,859 --> 00:16:06,899
<font color="#00ffff">to stay on the island and help us</font>
<font color="#00ffff">with the investigation.</font>

264
00:16:09,179 --> 00:16:10,739
<font color="#00ffff">Inspector?</font>

