00:17:27,219 --> 00:17:28,499
<font color="#ffff00">Commissioner.</font>

290
00:17:29,659 --> 00:17:32,259
<font color="#ffff00">I've updated Miss Reed</font>
<font color="#ffff00">on our second murder,</font>

