00:17:36,259 --> 00:17:39,059
<font color="#00ff00">I swear Stu never met this guy.</font>

294
00:17:39,099 --> 00:17:42,419
<font color="#ffff00">We've checked Mr Fullwell's texts,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">call register,</font>

