00:17:42,459 --> 00:17:45,419
<font color="#ffff00">emails, checked his bank account.</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Nothing.</font>

296
00:17:45,459 --> 00:17:47,259
<font color="#ffff00">The only thing we do have...</font>

297
00:17:49,539 --> 00:17:51,459
<font color="#ffff00">..is this.</font>

298
00:17:51,499 --> 00:17:54,659
<font color="#00ff00">DS Thomas mentioned about what</font>
<font color="#00ff00">Tony Hurst did,</font>

299
00:17:54,699 --> 00:17:58,259
<font color="#00ff00">about how he wrote that song,</font>
<font color="#00ff00">A Christmas Paradise, and...</font>

