00:19:16,739 --> 00:19:20,099
<font color="#00ff00">I wouldn't. That is not</font>
<font color="#00ff00">what happened.</font>

326
00:19:20,139 --> 00:19:24,259
<font color="#00ffff">Commissioner, Inspector, Sarge,</font>
<font color="#00ffff">the lab's just called.</font>

327
00:19:24,299 --> 00:19:27,619
<font color="#00ffff">There's something you might</font>
<font color="#00ffff">want to know.</font>

328
00:19:34,859 --> 00:19:36,139
Say that again.

329
00:19:36,179 --> 00:19:39,299
<font color="#00ffff">The bullets recovered from both</font>
<font color="#00ffff">victims' bodies have been compared,</font>

330
00:19:39,339 --> 00:19:41,739
<font color="#00ffff">and striation marks indicate...</font>

