00:20:25,099 --> 00:20:29,219
<font color="#00ff00">It's over. Stuart, you stupid idiot.</font>

338
00:20:35,379 --> 00:20:39,619
<font color="#ffff00">I feel I ought to say, on behalf of</font>
<font color="#ffff00">the rest of the island,</font>

