00:20:50,779 --> 00:20:52,979
I'm still trying to work out
what this one star is for.

343
00:20:53,019 --> 00:20:55,299
<font color="#ffff00">If you start to tire of its charms,</font>

344
00:20:55,339 --> 00:20:57,939
<font color="#ffff00">there is somewhere we can put you.</font>

