00:21:00,059 --> 00:21:01,059
Anyway...<font color="#ffff00">Ah...</font>

347
00:21:02,379 --> 00:21:06,299
<font color="#ffff00">If you don't mind me asking,</font>
<font color="#ffff00">how did you end up here?</font>

