00:21:12,339 --> 00:21:14,539
I guess with it being Christmas.

351
00:21:14,579 --> 00:21:17,699
<font color="#ffff00">I meant, um, Saint Marie.</font>

352
00:21:19,059 --> 00:21:21,099
Oh, right.

353
00:21:21,139 --> 00:21:22,859
